        "text": "This work is the first to explore the potential of prompting speech LMs in the domain of speech processing and reformulate speech processing tasks into speech-to-unit generation tasks, which can seamlessly integrate tasks such as speech classification, sequence generation, and speech generation within a single, unified prompting framework."
